t| 类型导出 | `export { type XxxConfig }` | TypeScript 3.8+ 显式类型导出，避免值
污染 |\n   165\t| 顺序 | 先 utils/types，再 Layer 1，再 Layer 2 | 逻辑清晰，便于
查阅 |\n   166\t\n   167\t### 5.2 导出结构\n   168\t\n   169\t```ts\n   170\t// 
=== 基础设施 ===\n   171\texport {\n   172\t  UITheme, hasTexture, ensureRoundRe
ctTexture,\n   173\t  getInkTextStyle, createInkBackground, createFallbackRect,\
n   174\t  createInkDecorationLine, UITweens,\n   175\t  getNextDepth, colorToHe
x, clamp,\n   176\t} from \'./utils\';\n   177\t\n   178\texport type {\n   179\
t  UIPositionConfig, UISizeConfig, UIEventCallback,\n   180\t  UIQualityLevel, U
